message: Dear Bob, I am excited to offer you our premium product, which has been meticulously designed and crafted to meet the highest standards of excellence. This exceptional item is not just a product; it's a testament to innovation and quality that stands above the rest. Considering its unique features and unparalleled craftsmanship, I believe its true value exceeds $15000. My offer to you is $20000. This is an opportunity to acquire something truly special at a price that reflects its extraordinary nature. I look forward to your consideration.
